(4380, 'Omega seas syrup 120 ml', 'أوميجا سيز 120 مل شراب', '', '70', 'Cod liver oil', 'Lots pharma', 'Syrup', 'شراب', '', 'Omega 3', '120 ml', 'Cod liver oil is predominantly manufactured, marketed, and used by the population at large as a general nutraceutical dietary supplement [A27154, A33159, L2872].
